rdf:Description.dc:title: RDA Unconstrained properties
rdf:Description.skos:note: Properties derived from RDA elements and relationship designators without specific or implicit restrictions to RDA entities.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abbreviatedTitle
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has abbreviated title
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a title that has been abbreviated for purposes of indexing or identification.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridged as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that shortens the source resource without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgementOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridgement of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been abridged, i.e., shortened without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation of the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridger
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has abridger
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by shortening or condensing the original resource but leaving the nature and content of the original resource substantially unchanged.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridger of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by shortening or condensing the original resource but leaving the nature and content of the original resource substantially unchanged to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that incorporates another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedInPartBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed in part by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that incorporates part of the content of another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorptionInPartOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption in part of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the resource that has been partially incorporated into another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorptionOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the resource that has been incorporated into another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstract
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstract
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that abbreviates the source resource in a brief, objective manner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracted in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource (an abstracting and indexing service) that abstracts the contents of a source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstract of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been abstracted, i.e., abbreviated in a brief, objective manner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractsFor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracts for
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose contents have been abstracted by an abstracting and indexing service.

rdf:Description.reg:name: academicDegree
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has academic degree
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a rank conferred as a guarantee of academic proficiency.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accessibilityContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accessibility content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to content that assists those with a sensory impairment in the greater understanding of content which their impairment prevents them fully seeing or hearing.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompaniedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is accompanied by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource issued with another resource, without any relationship to its content.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompanyingResourceRelationshipWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accompanying resource relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is an augmentation of, or is augmented by, or is complemented by, or accompanies, or is accompanied by the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: actor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has actor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a performer contributing to a resource by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: actorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is actor of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by acting as a cast member or player in a musical or dramatic presentation, etc. to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adaptation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been modified for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that modifies the source resource for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPicture
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a motion picture based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPictureScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of the screenplay for a motion picture, based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a radio program based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioScript
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio script
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of the script for a radio program, based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of the screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video, based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionProgram
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television program
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a television program based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of the screenplay for a television program, based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a video based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideoScreenplay
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video screenplay
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource consisting of the screenplay for a video, based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsMusicalTheatre
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as musical theatre
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a musical theatre resource based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsOpera
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as opera
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an opera based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addenda
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of brief additional material, less extensive than a supplement, but essential to the completeness of the text of the predominant resource; it is usually added at the end of the content, but is sometimes issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addendaTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource to which is added brief additional material, less extensive than a supplement, but essential to the completeness of the content of the resource; it is usually added at the end of the resource, but is sometimes issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: additionalScaleInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has additional scale information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to supplemental information about scale such as a statement of comparative measurements or limitation of the scale to particular parts of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addressee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has addressee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent to whom a resource or part of a resource is addressed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addresseeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addressee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent to whom a resource or part of a resource is addressed to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addressOfTheAgent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has address of the agent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the address of an agentâ€™s place of residence, business, or employer, headquarters or offices, or an e-mail or internet address.

rdf:Description.reg:name: affiliation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has affiliation
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a group with which an agent is affiliated or has been affiliated through employment, membership, cultural identity, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: agentHistory
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has agent history
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to biographical or historical information about the agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alsoIssuedAs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is also issued as
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource issued in a different format embodying the resource being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: alternateIdentity
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has alternate identity
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a pseudonymous or other identity assumed by the agent to the agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysedIn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysed in
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that examines the source resource to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysisOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysis of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been examined to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: animator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has animator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a moving image resource or computer program by giving apparent movement to inanimate objects or drawings.

rdf:Description.reg:name: animatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is animator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a moving image resource or computer program by giving apparent movement to inanimate objects or drawings to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: annotator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has annotator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who makes manuscript annotations on a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: annotatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is annotator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who makes manuscript annotations on a resource to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who appeals a lower courtâ€™s decision.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellantOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellant of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who appeals a lower courtâ€™s decision to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent against whom an appeal is taken.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appelleeOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appellee of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent against whom an appeal is taken to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appendix
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appendix
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that forms an augmenting part of another resource which is not essential to the completeness of the content, such as a list of references, statistical tables, and explanatory matter; it can either be material which comes at the end of the content of the predominant resource, or be issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appendixTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appendix to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that is augmented by another resource that consists of material that is not essential to the completeness of the content, such as a list of references, statistical tables, and explanatory matter; the augmenting resource can either come at the end of the content, or be issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appliedMaterial
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has applied material
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a physical or chemical substance applied to a base material of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: architect
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has architect
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating an architectural design, including a pictorial representation intended to show how a building, etc., will look when completed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: architectOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is architect of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating an architectural design, including a pictorial representation intended to show how a building, etc., will look when completed to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: arrangerOfMusic
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has arranger of music
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a musical resource by rewriting the composition for a medium of performance different from that for which the resource was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: arrangerOfMusicOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is arranger of music of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a musical resource by rewriting the composition for a medium of performance different from that for which the resource was originally intended to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has art director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent contributing to a resource by overseeing the artists and craftspeople who build the sets for moving image productions.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artDirectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is art director of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent contributing to a resource by overseeing the artists and craftspeople who build the sets for moving image productions to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has artist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a resource by conceiving, and often implementing, an original graphic design, drawing, painting, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artisticAndOrTechnicalCredit
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has artistic and/or technical credit
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a listing of agents, families, or corporate bodies making contributions to the artistic and/or technical production of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artistOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is artist of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a resource by conceiving, and often implementing, an original graphic design, drawing, painting, etc. to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: aspectRatio
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has aspect ratio
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the ratio of the width to the height of a moving image.

rdf:Description.reg:name: associatedInstitution
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has associated institution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an institution commonly associated with an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: augmentationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is augmentation of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource whose content is added to by another resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: augmentedBy
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is augmented by
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that adds to the content of a predominant resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: author
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has author
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a resource that is primarily textual in content, regardless of media type (e.g., printed text, spoken word, electronic text, tactile text) or genre (e.g., poems, novels, screenplays, blogs).

rdf:Description.reg:name: authorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is author of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a resource that is primarily textual in content, regardless of media type (e.g., printed text, spoken word, electronic text, tactile text) or genre (e.g., poems, novels, screenplays, blogs) to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: autographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has autographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent whose manuscript signature appears on a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: autographerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is autographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent whose manuscript signature appears on a resource to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: award
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has award
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a formal recognition of excellence, etc., given by an award- or prize-granting body, for the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: basedOn
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is based on
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource used as the source for a derivative resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: baseMaterial
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has base material
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the underlying physical material of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: baseMaterialForMicrofilmMicrofichePhotographicFilmAndMotionPictureFilm
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has base material for microfilm, microfiche, photographic film, and motion picture film
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the underlying physical material of a microfilm, microfiche, photographic film, or motion picture film resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: basisForLibretto
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is basis for libretto
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that consists of the text of an opera or other resource for the musical stage, or an oratorio, based on the source resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: binder

rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent who binds a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: binderOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is binder of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent who binds a resource to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: biographicalInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has biographical information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to information about the life or history of an agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: bookDesigner
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has book designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by being responsible for the entire graphic design of a book, including arrangement of type and illustration, choice of materials, and process used.

rdf:Description.reg:name: bookDesignerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is book designer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by being responsible for the entire graphic design of a book, including arrangement of type and illustration, choice of materials, and process used to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: bookFormat
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has book format
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to the result of folding a printed sheet to form a gathering of leaves (e.g., a sheet folded once to form a folio, twice to form a quarto, three times to form an octavo, etc.).

rdf:Description.reg:name: boundWith
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is bound with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a resource that has been bound within the same binding as the resource being described.

rdf:Description.reg:name: brailleEmbosser
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has braille embosser
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by embossing braille cells using a stylus, special embossing printer, or other device.

rdf:Description.reg:name: brailleEmbosserOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is braille embosser of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by embossing braille cells using a stylus, special embossing printer, or other device to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: broadcaster
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has broadcaster

rdf:Description.reg:name: broadcasterOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: broadcastStandard

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cadenza composed for

rdf:Description.reg:name: carrierType
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has carrier type
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to a categorization reflecting the format of the storage medium and housing of a carrier in combination with the type of intermediation device required to view, play, run, etc., the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cartographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has cartographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a map, atlas, globe, or other cartographic resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cartographerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cartographer of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a map, atlas, globe, or other cartographic resource to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: caster
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has caster
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by pouring a liquid or molten substance into a mold and leaving it to solidify to take the shape of the mold.

rdf:Description.reg:name: casterOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is caster of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent involved in manufacturing a resource by pouring a liquid or molten substance into a mold and leaving it to solidify to take the shape of the mold to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: catalogue

rdf:Description.reg:name: catalogueOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographer

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographerOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographyFor

rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has chronological designation of first issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to numbering presented in the form of a date (e.g., a year; year and month; month, day, and year) on the first issue or part of a sequence of numbering for a serial.

rdf:Description.reg:name: chronologicalDesignationOfLastIssueOrPartOfSequence
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has chronological designation of last issue or part of sequence
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to numbering presented in the form of a date (e.g., a year; year and month; month, day, and year) on the last issue or part of a sequence of numbering for a serial.

rdf:Description.reg:name: collectionRegistrarOf

rdf:Description.reg:name: collectorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is collector of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a curator who brings together resources from various sources that are then arranged, described, and cataloged as a collection to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryIn

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryOn

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentatorOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentator of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a performer contributing to a resource by providing interpretation, analysis, or a discussion of the subject matter on a recording, film, or other audiovisual medium to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: compiler
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has compiler
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a resource to an agent responsible for creating a new resource (e.g., a bibliography, a directory) by selecting, arranging, aggregating, and editing data, information, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: compilerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is compiler of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates an agent responsible for creating a new resource (e.g., a bibliography, a directory) by selecting, arranging, aggregating, and editing data, information, etc. to the resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: complementedBy
